nspamper
========

nspamper is a tiny daemon that takes care of updating a dynamic DNS name
using Bind9 NSupdates. You still have to tell it the IP, but no longer
have to take care of retransmits, ...

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Net::DNS
  Sys::Syslog;

